  "description": "<p>\n\t&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <strong>A fox and a goat</strong><br />\n\tAn unlucky fox fell into a well, It was quite deep, so he could not get out by himself.<br />\n\tA goat came. He asked the fox:&rdquo;what are you doing? The fox said : &quot;There will be no water, so I jumped down to get some water. Why don&rsquo;t you jump down, too?&quot;<br />\n\tThe goat jumped into the well.<br />\n\tBut the fox jumped on the goat&rsquo;s back and out of the well. &quot;Good-bye, friend,&quot; said the fox. &quot;Remember next time don&rsquo;t trust the advice of a man in difficulties.&quot;<br />\n\tThank you!<br />\n\t&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <strong>狐狸和山羊</strong><br />\n\t一只不走运的狐狸，失足掉到了井里。井很深，他无法跳出来。<br />\n\t一只山羊经过这里，便问狐狸在井下做什么。狐狸说：&ldquo;哦，你没有听说吗？这里将要大旱，因此我跳进来取水，为什么你不下来一起喝呢？&rdquo;<br />\n\t山羊相信了狐狸的话，就真的跳进井里。狐狸立即跳上山羊的背，又一跳，跳上了井沿。<br />\n\t&ldquo;再见，朋友，&rdquo;狐狸说，&ldquo;记住，不要相信一个身陷麻烦的人的建议。&nbsp;</p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p768986/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p768986\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p768746/\">趣味漫画：只有单身狗才懂的15件事 心酸萌</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p768779/\">2016两会这些热词不知道？口译别考了</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href